description: Who says ice cream trucks can't be cool, small and good for the environment? The Feverish concept is fun and exciting, we fuse fashion, art, music, social awareness and of course ice cream!  Feverish Ice Cream trucks have given the ice cream industry an Ice Cream Social Life. We strategically choose smaller vehicles for our fleets of ice cream trucks, so that our trucks have a smaller carbon foot print then most junkie ice cream trucks crawling around. Our hipster nightlife ice cream trucks carry unique ice cream, gourmet  fresh fruit bars and a tasty variety of healthy/vegan friendly ice cream.  Our new school twist on the childhood ice cream truck allows you to experience ice cream like never before!
name: Feverish Ice Cream
